    public class ComputeVariantsAndAddExperimentJob
extends de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.jobs.SequentialBlackboardInteractingJob<de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.mdsd.blackboard.MDSDBlackboard>
    This job computes all variation variants that should be executed in an experiment run. Furthermore, it adds vary and run experiment jobs for each considered variant.
